Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:08.47,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Happily, painfully... You're shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.76,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Glittering, shimmering...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:16.06,DTB-Default,Assistant,0,0,0,,Is she analyzing the Gullfinger wavelength of the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:20.34,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Hoshimi-sama, who usually doesn't say anything, spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:23.23,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,That in itself says volumes about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:31.33,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Indignation, compassion... Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:35.68,DTB-Default,Correspondent,0,0,0,,Abnormal behavior exhibited by the astronomer in charge of special duties was also observed five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:39.29,DTB-Default,Correspondent,0,0,0,,prior to the disappearance of South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:48.05,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Various intelligence agencies within the city have also taken the serial bombings into consideration and are at full alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.93,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Since these events have occurred before the upcoming solar maximum,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:56.02,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,one could say that the current situation may be the prelude to a tragic scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:02.88,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,As of 5 P.M. today, the Tokyo Metropolitan government has issued special security measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:07.71,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,including the implementation of a night curfew, for residents living in certain areas of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:15.10,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,These measures are to ensure the safety of the city's residents in light of the recent terrorist attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.58,DTB-Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,Areas subject to these...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:27.46,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Your sleeping face is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:36.80,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I've been trying to get Yin to locate Amber, but I lost contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.00,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,When I came here to check things out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:44.95,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:48.79,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.46,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.49,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hop in. You're in a rush, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:01.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Hoshimi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.28,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Although a gag order's in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:08.35,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,I wanted you to know, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:13.28,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,I sent you a list of the stars that were active during the explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:15.68,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Were contractors involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.61,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Wasn't it a series of retaliatory attacks between intelligence agencies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:22.23,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Information was leaked down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:28.78,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I don't believe that people who make their living in the underworld would resort to such a conspicuous method.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.07,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.34,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Why did Amber take Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:46.13,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I heard that you and her were on the same team in South America until she left the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:49.06,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What happened between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.26,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.61,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:07.95,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,November... If anything happens... Police... Misaki's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.18,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.25,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,He didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.20,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Do you know where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:17.79,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,I always know where my partners are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.69,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Tell me along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.22,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.77,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.63,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Good morning. Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.76,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.37,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:39.90,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.70,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,No need to rush. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.44,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be my remuneration if the milk wasn't hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.41,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.51,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,but would you mind if I had a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.56,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,They're in my left suit pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:07.22,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I'm not allowed to make physical contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.75,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You're an excellent contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.37,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You were able to avoid the scorching heat by making a split-second decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:20.44,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate a smoke more than a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:28.45,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Did you know that cigarette smoke is more hazardous to those around the smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:36.31,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,The amount of the carcinogen dimethylnitrosamine present in direct smoke is between 5.3 and 43 nanograms,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.73,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,while there are between 680...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.44,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:47.27,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see what happens to a contractor who doesn't complete his remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.86,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Do they really melt like butter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.35,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.73,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,There was a vending machine on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.48,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.87,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.25,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What an admirable young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:13.63,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,managing to study whenever you're not bombing buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.89,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,It gives me a strange feeling for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.82,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amber taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.66,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,At first, I thought it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:28.77,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,You can't reach out to people with mere words since they're just enumerations of syllables,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.64,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,but Amber said that wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:38.51,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'm studying every day because Amber told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.63,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'd do anything for Amber's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:47.40,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'd even destroy this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.51,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:55.62,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You'll have to sit still for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.91,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Those were orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.94,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I can't let you meet Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.38,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.36,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hey, Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.30,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.02,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:19.77,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,but it's partly your fault for constantly not listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.65,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:28.23,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You're the one who's going to die if you don't follow the syndicate's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.43,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't make me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.48,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Huang, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.90,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Alley cats should shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.11,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(962,329)}Episode Sixteen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(851,599)}Memories of Betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,649)}in an Amber Smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,710)}(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.15,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:07.74,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Why would a contractor like you work for human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.87,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,We're the chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:18.36,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,They're afraid of us because they can't sign contracts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.53,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,which makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:24.40,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,An existence with newly acquired powers has emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:29.83,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,An existence fit to establish a new world order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.89,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Is that part of Amber's manifesto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.97,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amber wouldn't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:46.92,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I was told that the tragedy that took place in South America had to be repeated in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.92,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.19,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:54.61,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,but it must be important since Amber was the one who said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.93,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You'd probably understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:04.32,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,The reason for our group's conception and course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:10.81,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,We, the Evening Primrose, invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.37,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:17.89,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What kind of benefits do I receive if I join your little club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.52,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,The future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:26.37,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,In your situation, you don't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:30.03,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Decide rationally, November 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:45.43,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me. I just remembered saying the same thing to a certain contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.55,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What do you think he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.37,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,He attacked me with everything he had,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:57.28,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,even though he only had a slight chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.86,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I couldn't rationalize why a contractor like that would exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:10.39,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,His train of thought and principles of life... The more I thought about it, the more I became confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:15.85,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,How touching. Are you going to follow his example?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:21.62,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,No, I take pride in being a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.40,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,That's why I've come to a rational decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:24.76,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.82,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.41,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Freeze! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.52,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Slowly put your hands behind your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:46.95,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,You're like a knight in shining armor, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:47.81,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.05,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The ones responsible for the explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.72,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.15,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Your partner led me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.16,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.88,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes, July-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:07.43,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You'll definitely come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:12.71,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,You'll definitely seek us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:32.05,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Shining across the Milky Way... Yearning, yet distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:37.83,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,If that is what fate has decided, I will not hinder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.06,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Nobody will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.26,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I couldn't make him join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.07,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.25,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Where is Amber?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.71,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I already told you. She's waiting for the final key.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.35,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Who could she be waiting for while leaving me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.49,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Is it someone that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.86,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.34,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.63,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.49,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I'll tell her what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:15.64,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Head to the second meeting point. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.54,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,That was an order from Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:43.08,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,There was one time when he actually laughed from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:48.10,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,His sweet smile captivated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.06,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,That's when I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.47,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,"You really did it this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:12:00.66,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I felt as if I could do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:06.19,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I'd do anything to see that smile again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.14,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I'm sure you feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.28,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.08,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.08,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Look after him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.51,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.27,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.81,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.76,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,If you're going that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.78,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,You must be the one called Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.77,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amber always talks about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.63,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.81,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,It was the first time I was able to say it without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.58,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,That's why I was happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.78,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,but I'm not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.91,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,This is what you would call jealousy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.83,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amber always talks about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.81,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,That's why I won't let you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.04,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I said I won't let you see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.19,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.12,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Good boys shouldn't be up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.17,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.13,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Go after the man who ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.58,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,That ability... He's the contractor you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.02,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:58.79,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I have to teach that mischievous boy a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.66,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Don't worry. July's by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.06,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Hurry, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.46,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.52,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,If you want to fight me that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.86,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.86,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.34,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:39.47,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I set traps on everything you're capable of freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:41.35,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,You won't be able to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.17,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Come and get me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.21,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be an excellent contractor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.59,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I don't need you, Hei, or Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.48,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'm the contractor best suited for Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.90,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.81,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Show me! Prove that you're stronger than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.42,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:28.64,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,See? I'm far better than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.19,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,You don't need anyone else, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.78,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I'm the best, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.91,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Amber?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.29,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:56.67,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:06.40,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Are you hurt? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.15,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You've grown, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.17,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I don't have any intention of forgiving a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:23.67,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Before I kill you, there's something I need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.13,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What happened during that incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.23,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Where did my sister go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:31.43,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything to say before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.26,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Like "it's been a while",
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.36,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,or "you look as pretty as ever".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Answer me, Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.61,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Do you want to see Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.98,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Should I take you to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.28,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.80,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Somewhere far, yet really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.88,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Come with me, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.49,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll take you to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:04.08,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,but the city lights might vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.69,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.59,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't screw around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.01,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.42,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.28,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Move, Amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:53.75,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Hei, I've traveled very far,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.77,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,even across the plane of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:00.83,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.75,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Always, always...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.26,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.11,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:21.86,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:28.16,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,There's a limit on your remuneration, so use it wisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.17,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Wasn't that the right time to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.66,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Star-sama, do not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:42.26,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,It is not yet time to radiate. Your time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.90,DTB-Default,Primrose A,0,0,0,,How did everything go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.92,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,I was able to split the enemy lines, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.69,DTB-Default,Primrose B,0,0,0,,All we need to do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:18.94,DTB-Default,Primrose C,0,0,0,,Are you sure we need that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:24.70,DTB-Default,Primrose A,0,0,0,,Yes, if we want the Evening Primrose to reach full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.40,DTB-Default,Amagiri,0,0,0,,Maki should have arrived before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.11,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,No, he won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:40.39,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,I don't like that word because it makes me feel lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:46.90,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,but I have to say good-bye properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.01,DTB-Default,Maki,0,0,0,,Amber...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:58.07,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,What's this? Revenge on my behalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.56,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.12,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Neither was your joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.68,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Huang, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:23.39,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yeah. It looks like I'm the one with nine lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Did he hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:32.33,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,A contractor like him, fucking around with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, you realize that what was thought to be unattainable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,is close at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:50.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a happiness not destined for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Serenity and trivial conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Being both happy and sad over petty things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,crying over concerns not worth bothering with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:03.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Too sullied to live in such a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:08.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you understand that those days will not go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:09.23,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Seventeen A Love Song Sung from a Trash Heap... (Part One)